      • addPurchase

        public boolean addPurchase(double purchaseAmount)
        Reports whether a transaction made on a customer account is valid or not, i.e. if the purchase puts the customer over his or her available credit limit, this method will return false, returning true if the purchase does not put the customer over his or her available credit limit
        Parameters:
        purchaseAmount - amount of a new purchase to be added to this account
        Returns:
        boolean
